<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> القِيَامُ فِي فَرْضِهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَالتَّكْبِيرَاتُ الأَرْبَعُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
